1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:03,810
(Episode 72)

2
00:00:14,990 --> 00:00:15,990
Who are you?

3
00:00:28,630 --> 00:00:29,630
Oh Jang Mi?

4
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:52,360
You're Oh Jang Mi.

5
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:54,890
That's right. It's me, Oh Jang Mi.

6
00:00:55,630 --> 00:00:58,330
The very same Oh Jang Mi
you tried so desperately to kill.

7
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:02,070
But I didn't die,
and here I am, alive and well.

8
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:05,400
So? How does it feel to see me?

9
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:09,310
Oh Jang Mi. How are you here?

10
00:01:11,310 --> 00:01:12,310
Oh Jang Mi.

11
00:01:13,210 --> 00:01:15,650
You had me completely fooled
all this time.

12
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:20,390
You were awake, but you were just acting,
pretending to be in a coma?

13
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:25,390
And then you teamed up with your brother,
leaked that video to get me in trouble?

14
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:29,260
- Trouble?
- How dare you waltz in here?

15
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:32,730
You think this is going to make me
bat an eye?

16
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:34,030
Really?

17
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,370
Then I'll show you what torment
I have in store for you.

18
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:39,400
Struggling will be useless.

19
00:01:44,110 --> 00:01:45,710
You shameless, evil witch.

20
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:47,480
Shut up! Watch your mouth!

21
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:55,750
- No one can come in right now.
- Mom. It's me.

22
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:57,190
Your daughter, Ma Seo Rin.

23
00:01:57,990 --> 00:01:58,990
Seo Rin?

24
00:02:01,890 --> 00:02:03,560
Didn't you call for me?

25
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,170
Oh Jang Mi.

26
00:02:08,530 --> 00:02:09,970
Did you tell Seo Rin to come?

27
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,670
Why? Are you scared?

28
00:02:12,300 --> 00:02:15,170
You're scared to death
that Seo Rin and I might meet, aren't you?

29
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:18,640
Seo Rin. Come back later.

30
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,650
I'm busy right now, so come back later.

31
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:22,450
Why? Open the door.

32
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:25,050
I want to see Seo Rin, too. Come on.

33
00:02:25,050 --> 00:02:26,150
Shut up.

34
00:02:27,950 --> 00:02:29,220
Got it, Seo Rin?

35
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:32,120
Shit! Fine.

36
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:33,390
I'm leaving.

37
00:02:41,530 --> 00:02:43,300
- You're here, Chairman.
- Yes.

38
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:47,540
So, Lawyer Kang,
how are you liking the company?

39
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:50,140
It's been great.
Thank you for looking out for me, sir.

40
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,840
- Are you here to see CEO Chae?
- Yes.

41
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:54,910
I'll show you in.

42
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,050
Thanks.

43
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:03,790
What brings the Chairman here?

44
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:06,990
Don't tell me
he's here to see the CEO Chae.

45
00:03:08,260 --> 00:03:10,090
I wonder if the CEO Chae
knows he's coming.

46
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,670
Why so flustered?

47
00:03:14,330 --> 00:03:18,270
It's a shame. A reunion with my twin,
Ma Seo Rin, would've been nice.

48
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:21,440
I guess Chae Hwa Young
didn't want a twin reunion?

49
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:22,540
Shut up!

50
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:25,040
You really have a death wish.

51
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:28,580
Who do you think you are,
crawling in here and spouting nonsense?

52
00:03:28,650 --> 00:03:29,650
You have some nerve.

53
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:39,660
Ma'am, Chairman Ma is on his way now.

54
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:42,060
What? The Chairman?

55
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:45,160
What perfect timing.

56
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:47,600
I should say hello.
He is our grandfather, after all.

57
00:03:48,070 --> 00:03:50,900
Since I missed my reunion with Seo Rin,
I should at least see our grandfather.

58
00:03:50,970 --> 00:03:52,040
No, Kang Hyuk.

59
00:03:52,370 --> 00:03:54,910
Stop him, now!
The Chairman can't come in here!

60
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:58,040
Why? It'll be so much fun if he sees me.
Why stop him?

61
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,310
I said, shut up!

62
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:02,380
You're trying to cover the sky
with your hand.

63
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,280
Do you really think
you can stop what's coming?

64
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,080
You're finished.

65
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:09,490
Kang Hyuk, you have to stop the Chairman.
He can't come in here right now.

66
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:12,460
Oh Jang Mi is in here.
Keep the Chairman out at all costs!

67
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,490
If you were going to be this terrified,

68
00:04:15,890 --> 00:04:18,560
why did you steal my sister away
from our mother?

69
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,870
How could a human being
do something like that?

70
00:04:21,530 --> 00:04:24,870
To hide it, you had our father killed
and even tried to kill me!

71
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:29,440
I will never forgive you.
I will risk everything to bring you down.

72
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:31,240
I don't care if I fall
into the fires of torment with you!

73
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,710
Brace yourself.

74
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:37,680
You sure can run your mouth.
You're all talk.

75
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:40,450
What can someone like you possibly do?

76
00:04:41,450 --> 00:04:42,490
Don't get cocky.

77
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,560
My patience has its limits.

78
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:48,130
Move. I'm going to see the Chairman now.
I said move, Chae Hwa Young!

79
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:49,190
No!

80
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:52,830
You can't, Oh Jang Mi.
You're never leaving this room.

81
00:04:57,940 --> 00:05:00,940
I should get going.
I have some documents to review.

82
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,540
Alright.

83
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:04,340
You should come over to my house sometime.

84
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:06,680
Yes, I would be honored
if you'd invite me.

85
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,010
All right.

86
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,220
Chairman.

87
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,660
Hey...

88
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:23,530
Chairman, it's not a good time to go in.

89
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:25,360
What? Why not?

90
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:29,500
CEO Chae is on a call
with the Dream Resort fund.

91
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:32,200
Manager Lee.
What do you think you're doing?

92
00:05:32,570 --> 00:05:34,540
Stopping the Chairman
just for a video call?

93
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,080
What's the reason?

94
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:42,050
If you go in now,
you'll just confirm the rumors are true.

95
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:44,350
- Rumors?
- The rumors that CEO Chae...

96
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:46,220
will be fired over the recent controversy.

97
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:50,590
The investors called personally
to confirm whether it was true.

98
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,590
If you go in at this exact moment,

99
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,930
they'll think the rumors are true
and pull their investment.

100
00:05:56,030 --> 00:05:58,560
What is all of this?

101
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:01,970
The CEO of our hotel can't even earn
the trust of her own investors.

102
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,400
Chairman...

103
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,740
You shameless creature.

104
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:15,310
Are you that scared the Chairman
will find out your true colors?

105
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:17,420
- Let go of me!
- Does it hurt?

106
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,820
You think this is painful?

107
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:21,350
My father suffered far more when he died!

108
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,320
Don't mess with me, Oh Jang Mi.

109
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,160
What could you possibly do?

110
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:31,530
You really think you're in my league?

111
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,830
Funny you should ask.

112
00:06:33,030 --> 00:06:34,570
Want to see if I'm a match for you?

113
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:36,400
Should I call the Chairman back in now?

114
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,340
Don't make me laugh.

115
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:42,770
Do you really think I'd bat an eye,
no matter what you try to pull?

116
00:06:42,970 --> 00:06:43,980
Is that so?

117
00:06:44,910 --> 00:06:46,010
All right, then.

118
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,710
We'll leave it at that for today.

119
00:06:51,450 --> 00:06:52,450
Oh, right.

120
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:56,620
Chae Hwa Young.

121
00:06:57,290 --> 00:07:01,130
I think I'd enjoy watching you suffer
for a long, long time.

122
00:07:02,030 --> 00:07:03,030
What did you just say?

123
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:04,630
You little brat!

124
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,730
Don't you dare touch me!

125
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:09,030
I can turn this place into a bloodbath.

126
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:11,200
If that happens, it's over for you too.

127
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:14,370
I'll be taking you down with me.
Is that what you want?

128
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,580
Listen carefully, Chae Hwa Young.

129
00:07:18,110 --> 00:07:21,380
I'll make you spend the rest of your life
paying for my father's death.

130
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,950
It's no fun
if I just finish you off today.

131
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:27,020
I'm going to torment you
and slowly bleed you dry.

132
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:28,650
Just you wait.

133
00:07:33,890 --> 00:07:36,960
Consider this just a warning for today.

134
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:39,160
You'd better stay on your toes.

135
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,270
From now on,

136
00:07:41,330 --> 00:07:43,800
I'm going to make your life
a living torment.

137
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,040
Fine.

138
00:07:46,570 --> 00:07:48,310
Show me what you've got.

139
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:50,440
Actually, just you wait.

140
00:07:50,910 --> 00:07:52,740
Because you'll be joining
your father soon enough.

141
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,960
- Ouch, that hurts.
- Oh, dear.

142
00:08:12,030 --> 00:08:13,030
Here you go.

143
00:08:14,730 --> 00:08:16,000
Be careful not to get caught.

144
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:18,040
Go quickly, before CEO Chae finds you.

145
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,140
Okay.

146
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,840
Your hat.

147
00:08:25,780 --> 00:08:26,780
All right, then.

148
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:36,650
How on earth did Oh Jang Mi get in here?

149
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:39,020
Don't tell me...

150
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:42,090
that was Seo Rin
pretending to be Oh Jang Mi?

151
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,100
I need to find out right now.

152
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,070
Where's Director Ma?

153
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,380
(Director Ma Seo Rin)

154
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:58,510
What?

155
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:03,010
I'm right here.
I was just picking up my pen.

156
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:06,020
Have you been there the whole time?

157
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:09,250
Yes. Why?

158
00:09:09,890 --> 00:09:10,890
Never mind.

159
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:30,640
A little more forward.

160
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:34,010
Stop.

161
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,350
So the little rat was hiding right there.

162
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:48,830
What have you been doing all this time?

163
00:09:49,290 --> 00:09:52,560
What were you doing
while Oh Jang Mi was here making a scene?

164
00:09:52,700 --> 00:09:53,760
I'm sorry.

165
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:56,230
What kind of men are working for you?

166
00:09:56,230 --> 00:09:58,070
Am I supposed to trust these incompetents?

167
00:09:59,070 --> 00:10:00,140
I'm sorry, ma'am.

168
00:10:01,010 --> 00:10:02,510
Oh Jang Mi!

169
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,540
That little brat...

170
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:08,650
left here after threatening
to drive me to my grave.

171
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:12,520
That tenacious little brat came here
just to mock me!

172
00:10:13,450 --> 00:10:15,650
Find her. Find Oh Jang Mi right now!

173
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,590
Find her and drag her to me!

174
00:10:18,590 --> 00:10:19,590
Understood.

175
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:33,040
All right, coffee time, everyone.

176
00:10:33,540 --> 00:10:35,310
Goodness, Lawyer Kang.

177
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:36,870
You gave me mine first.

178
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:39,240
- I'm so touched.
- Oh, well...

179
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:41,280
I just gave it to you first
because you were the closest.

180
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,420
Here you go.

181
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,880
Thank you.

182
00:10:56,130 --> 00:10:59,230
Lawyer Kang,
could you take a look at this for me?

183
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:00,300
Sure.

184
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:05,040
- One second.
- Okay.

185
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:11,680
Did Geum Soon get away safely?

186
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:18,750
Yes, she took the taxi
I had waiting for her.

187
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:20,920
I waited until she was safely away
before coming up.

188
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:22,920
Thank you for your help, Baek Ho.

189
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:26,560
Chae Hwa Young must be dead set
on finding me by now.

190
00:11:26,890 --> 00:11:30,190
I'm worried about what CEO Chae might do,
so be extra careful.

191
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:31,330
My love.

192
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:36,700
Oh my.

193
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,620
Mrs. Yang!

194
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:57,050
Why are you rushing in
like you've got something to hide?

195
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:59,360
Goodness, what are you talking about?

196
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,890
I just really have to use the restroom.

197
00:12:01,330 --> 00:12:02,330
Wait a minute. Stop!

198
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:06,860
And what's this?

199
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,700
Hey, why are you touching my things?

200
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:11,340
I'm entitled to some privacy, you know.

201
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:13,140
Privacy?

202
00:12:14,370 --> 00:12:15,470
Wait.

203
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:17,910
What is it now?

204
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:20,980
You said you had to use the restroom.
So why are you running to the kitchen?

205
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:22,710
That's suspicious.

206
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:29,420
What have you been up to lately?

207
00:12:29,850 --> 00:12:32,890
You're acting suspicious, Geum Soon.

208
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:34,590
Please. You find everything suspicious.

209
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:36,860
I have bladder problems,

210
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:39,230
so I was getting the spare underwear
I had stashed.

211
00:12:39,530 --> 00:12:40,530
Satisfied?

212
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:47,300
She could've just said so.
Why does she have to shout?

213
00:12:49,110 --> 00:12:52,140
Nowadays, workers act
like they own the place!

214
00:12:52,610 --> 00:12:53,610
Darn it.

215
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:55,950
Thank you, come again!

216
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:58,350
(Bomdama)

217
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:06,090
- Hey.
- Hey, is it a good time to talk?

218
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:09,530
The lunch rush just ended.
I can finally breathe.

219
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:11,060
How's Mom doing?

220
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:16,300
- Was Jang Mi okay today?
- See? This is what I'm talking about.

221
00:13:16,570 --> 00:13:20,170
I knew you'd keep bringing up Jang Mi.
That's why I wasn't going to tell you.

222
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:22,270
What did I do?

223
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:25,580
Did I broadcast to the world
that Jang Mi is impersonating Seo Rin?

224
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:28,150
Darn it.
You might as well use a megaphone!

225
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:30,650
How am I supposed to tell you any secrets?

226
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:33,580
Anyway, if Jang Mi gets in trouble,
it'll be all your fault!

227
00:13:34,490 --> 00:13:35,490
Hey, Oh Tae Pyung!

228
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:40,020
Unbelievable. What did I even do?

229
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:43,830
I'm as tight-lipped as they come.

230
00:13:47,430 --> 00:13:48,430
Tae Pyung.

231
00:13:48,930 --> 00:13:50,630
Bo Ra sings so well.

232
00:13:51,770 --> 00:13:54,410
I'll sing a song
I learned in kindergarten.

233
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:56,640
Okay, let's hear what our Bo Ra learned.

234
00:13:57,410 --> 00:14:00,740
- You have to clap before she sings.
- Okay! You're so cute!

235
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:06,050
<i>Three bears live in a house</i>

236
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:09,920
<i>Papa Bear, Mama Bear, and Baby Bear</i>

237
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:13,890
<i>Papa Bear is chubby</i>

238
00:14:14,330 --> 00:14:17,760
<i>Mama Bear is skinny</i>

239
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:19,130
<i>Baby Bear...</i>

240
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:22,330
At least her mom and Bo Ra are having fun.

241
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:27,540
<i>- Way to go</i>!
- Bo Ra is such a good singer!

242
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:29,810
- You're the best!
- The best!

243
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:35,010
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

244
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:37,310
(Actress Chae Hwa Young Joins Dream Group,
Becomes CEO!)

245
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:42,690
While I was in the hospital,
fighting for my life with leukemia,

246
00:14:43,190 --> 00:14:44,920
you were living it up like this?

247
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,860
And now you come looking for me?

248
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:50,490
Why? Why on earth?

249
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:53,300
I'll never forgive you.

250
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:57,100
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

251
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,240
- Hi, Mom.
- Jun Ho.

252
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,410
You left without any breakfast.

253
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,580
Have you eaten?

254
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:09,150
Yes, I have, Mom. Don't worry.

255
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:11,980
You didn't seem to have
much of an appetite,

256
00:15:12,250 --> 00:15:14,020
so I was thinking of packing you a lunch.

257
00:15:15,450 --> 00:15:18,890
- It's fine, Mom. You don't have to.
- By the way...

258
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:22,490
So what's the latest
on your marriage to Director Ma?

259
00:15:22,890 --> 00:15:23,890
What?

260
00:15:24,190 --> 00:15:26,960
With CEO Chae bringing it up,

261
00:15:27,230 --> 00:15:30,470
it seems like nothing's happened
since she mentioned it.

262
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:35,110
So you really don't want
to marry Director Ma?

263
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:38,410
Or do you want to,

264
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:43,150
but you're hesitant since your dad objects
and the terms aren't ideal?

265
00:15:43,780 --> 00:15:46,480
I just want to know
what you're really thinking.

266
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:49,520
Hello? Jun Ho, are you listening?

267
00:15:54,890 --> 00:15:56,030
What am I thinking?

268
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:58,900
This isn't really a conversation
for the phone, is it?

269
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:03,230
It's not like we ever get a chance
to discuss this at home.

270
00:16:04,470 --> 00:16:07,200
It just popped into my head while working,
so I called.

271
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,940
Anyway, get back to work.

272
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:11,340
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

273
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:15,880
I'm wondering the same thing, Mom.

274
00:16:17,610 --> 00:16:19,120
This woman, Chae Hwa Young,

275
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:23,250
why is she trying to set me up
to marry Director Ma?

276
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:34,130
I have something I need to say.

277
00:16:35,230 --> 00:16:37,500
Go on. What is it?

278
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:38,900
Do you really...

279
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:42,210
want Director Ma and me to get married?

280
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:46,380
It's funny you're asking so seriously
all of a sudden.

281
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:50,410
Did you think I was just playing games
with you all this time...

282
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:52,820
when I said I wanted you as my son-in-law?

283
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:55,950
I've told you already.

284
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:58,890
I want Seo Rin and you to join forces...

285
00:16:59,420 --> 00:17:01,460
and take over Dream.

286
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:04,400
I must have told you this countless times,

287
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:08,470
so why is it that
you still don't believe me?

288
00:17:08,470 --> 00:17:09,600
That's right.

289
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:13,340
You've humiliated and tormented me
more times than I can count.

290
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:15,970
It's not something
I can just easily believe.

291
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:18,180
Whether you look at my background
or anything else,

292
00:17:18,710 --> 00:17:20,040
as a marriage partner for Director Ma,

293
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:22,450
I don't think I'm a suitable match.

294
00:17:23,450 --> 00:17:26,380
Why do you keep twisting my words
like this?

295
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,390
Can't you just take me at my word?

296
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:30,420
I can only take you at your word
if you're trustworthy.

297
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,460
- General Manager Kang.
- Are you planning...

298
00:17:32,790 --> 00:17:34,930
to make me CEO and put me in your place,

299
00:17:35,930 --> 00:17:37,830
only to throw me in prison this time?

300
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:41,500
We don't match,
but yet you want me to marry her?

301
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,600
How can I possibly believe you?

302
00:17:43,530 --> 00:17:45,000
You have to give me a reason to trust you.

303
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:47,340
It just doesn't make any sense.

304
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:51,480
Why on earth?

305
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:55,210
Why do you want me to marry your daughter?

306
00:17:55,950 --> 00:17:57,210
I'll need more time to think about it.

307
00:17:58,150 --> 00:18:00,020
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

308
00:18:09,130 --> 00:18:10,130
Jun Ho.

309
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:12,730
What am I going to do?

310
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:18,800
(Director Ma Seo Rin)

311
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:30,210
Who is this child?

312
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:33,920
Why was Chae Hwa Young
crying over this photo?

313
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:38,920
This is my mom's hairpin.

314
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:43,090
If that pearl hairpin wasn't my mom's,

315
00:18:43,890 --> 00:18:45,930
then that means the child is connected
to Chae Hwa Young.

316
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:50,100
Then why on earth was that hairpin
pinned to the baby's clothes?

317
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:03,350
What's going on?

318
00:19:03,610 --> 00:19:04,750
Chae Hwa Young.

319
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:07,220
What could possibly be making her so sad?

320
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:09,290
It's so unlike her.

321
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:35,310
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

322
00:19:43,090 --> 00:19:45,390
This is the photo
Chae Hwa Young was crying over.

323
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:48,630
Why was she crying
over this picture again?

324
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:51,230
Just who is the baby in this photo?

325
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:04,470
May 29, 1990.

326
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:08,280
Must be the baby's birthday.

327
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:13,120
(Wonpyeong Photo Studio)

328
00:20:13,180 --> 00:20:15,150
(15 Wonpyeong-ri, Giyeon-myeon,
Jeongdong-gun, Gyeonggi)

329
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:22,530
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

330
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:35,040
So what happened to that brat, Oh Jang Mi?

331
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:37,270
She vanished without a trace.

332
00:20:38,310 --> 00:20:39,340
What do you mean?

333
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:44,350
Because that brat, Oh Jang Mi, showed up,
I almost ran into Chairman Ma.

334
00:20:44,410 --> 00:20:45,720
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

335
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:48,120
That old man couldn't have come
because he knows something, right?

336
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,320
He always shows up
at the worst possible times.

337
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,590
But for Oh Jang Mi to show up
here so brazenly,

338
00:20:53,120 --> 00:20:54,390
could that mean she has an accomplice?

339
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:58,000
Of course there's someone helping her.

340
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,230
Oh Tae Pyung and Kang Baek Ho.

341
00:21:09,540 --> 00:21:10,770
Ta-da!

342
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:15,050
Presenting
the Kang Nam Bong special tofu stew!

343
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:16,680
Eat up, honey.

344
00:21:18,150 --> 00:21:20,150
- Honey.
- Yes?

345
00:21:21,020 --> 00:21:23,820
I have a confession to make.

346
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:27,390
If you promise that you won't get mad
when you hear it,

347
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:28,890
I'll tell you.

348
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:33,500
What? How can I promise not to get mad
if I don't know what it is?

349
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:37,500
You're right. You can be mad.
It's my fault.

350
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:40,700
- Honey.
- The thing is...

351
00:21:42,170 --> 00:21:43,470
The other day,

352
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:45,110
I followed you.

353
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:48,110
- What?
- It's just,

354
00:21:49,050 --> 00:21:52,520
you've been so quick to snap at me lately,

355
00:21:52,580 --> 00:21:54,520
and you're always so irritable...

356
00:21:55,090 --> 00:21:57,190
that I started to wonder
if you were seeing someone else.

357
00:21:57,950 --> 00:21:59,120
I couldn't help but be suspicious.

358
00:22:03,990 --> 00:22:05,030
So?

359
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:07,200
But where does a workaholic like you go?

360
00:22:08,170 --> 00:22:10,400
Nowhere but the Dream Hotel.

361
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:15,770
I saw you in CEO Chae's office
working hard,

362
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:18,580
and I'm sorry I ever doubted you.

363
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:22,610
I know you would never, ever...

364
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:25,020
betray me or do anything like that.

365
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:28,820
I guess my professional habits
got the better of me.

366
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:34,360
Goodness.

367
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,690
Are you mad, honey?

368
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,260
What?

369
00:22:39,860 --> 00:22:41,900
No, I was just feeling ashamed of myself.

370
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:45,900
I'm sorry for giving you
a reason to be suspicious.

371
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:48,710
I'll try not to be
so irritable from now on.

372
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:53,640
You saying that just makes me
feel even worse.

373
00:22:56,050 --> 00:22:57,280
Here, let me get you some.

374
00:22:58,320 --> 00:23:01,820
Here you go.
Kang Nam Bong's signature tofu stew.

375
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:05,060
It's to die for.

376
00:23:07,690 --> 00:23:09,560
What? You're saying something's off
with Chae Hwa Young?

377
00:23:09,890 --> 00:23:13,330
Yes. For one thing, it seems like
she and Jun Ho are fighting.

378
00:23:13,900 --> 00:23:17,730
But the weirdest part was
seeing her cry over a baby picture.

379
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:21,840
- Her, crying? That's unbelievable.
- I know, right?

380
00:23:22,140 --> 00:23:24,370
I have absolutely no idea
why she'd be crying.

381
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:28,080
Here, take a look at this photo.

382
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:31,210
Looks like it could be a boy.

383
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:34,950
Maybe she had a baby, and it died?

384
00:23:35,420 --> 00:23:36,820
She said the name was Ha Neul.

385
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:38,050
That's possible.

386
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:40,920
So is that why she stole
Seo Rin from your mother?

387
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:44,260
Either way, CEO Chae is full of secrets.

388
00:23:44,260 --> 00:23:46,160
She's like an onion with endless layers.

389
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:49,100
And to think my father
is falling for a woman like that...

390
00:23:49,630 --> 00:23:52,770
If we keep digging into Chae Hwa Young,
we'll find her Achilles' heel.

391
00:23:53,670 --> 00:23:55,570
And that might be the opening we need.

392
00:23:56,510 --> 00:23:58,680
Right. We don't know what that is yet,
but...

393
00:24:05,050 --> 00:24:07,350
Geum Soon, you did great today.

394
00:24:07,520 --> 00:24:09,690
It was a total thrill. So exciting.

395
00:24:09,990 --> 00:24:12,460
- So our plan worked?
- It did.

396
00:24:12,990 --> 00:24:16,460
You should've seen how terrified
Chae Hwa Young's face looked.

397
00:24:17,330 --> 00:24:18,860
I have to admit, it was pretty satisfying.

398
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:23,930
By the way, Geum Soon,
do you know anything about this photo?

399
00:24:24,370 --> 00:24:25,800
What's this? A baby picture?

400
00:24:26,170 --> 00:24:28,670
I've seen it in CEO Chae's room before,

401
00:24:28,670 --> 00:24:31,110
and I saw her crying
over this same photo again today.

402
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:33,740
- Who on earth is this baby?
- What?

403
00:24:34,040 --> 00:24:35,880
She was crying over this baby picture?

404
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:39,080
Could it be her son?

405
00:24:40,120 --> 00:24:41,220
No way.

406
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:42,820
You think?

407
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:46,790
That's true. If she had her own son,
why would she steal a twin?

408
00:24:48,730 --> 00:24:49,860
Then again...

409
00:24:50,230 --> 00:24:51,260
Look at this part, too.

410
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:54,970
May 29, 1990?

411
00:24:55,570 --> 00:24:58,100
- What's this?
- I think it's the baby's birthdate,

412
00:24:58,300 --> 00:25:01,770
so I was wondering
if you know anyone with this birthday.

413
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:04,240
Not that I know of.

414
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:09,210
Wait. There's a studio name here.
Wonpyeong Photo Studio.

415
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:11,780
It must be a studio in Wonpyeong-ri.

416
00:25:12,580 --> 00:25:14,320
Yes, you're right.

417
00:25:24,260 --> 00:25:28,600
Seo Rin, you've become an early bird.
You were never a morning person.

418
00:25:28,770 --> 00:25:30,030
I guess I'm just growing up.

419
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:32,170
Right, Grandfather?

420
00:25:32,170 --> 00:25:35,170
I have to learn the business
if I'm going to take over Dream.

421
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:39,880
Absolutely. I'm so proud of you
for finally coming to your senses.

422
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:54,990
What's the status?
Have the DNA results come in yet?

423
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:58,800
I called, and they sent it by courier.
It should be here any minute.

424
00:25:58,860 --> 00:26:01,260
You should've just had them text it.

425
00:26:01,260 --> 00:26:03,100
Just wait. It'll be here any minute.

426
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:08,140
Hong Ju, I'm getting giddy
just imagining her face turning pale.

427
00:26:09,970 --> 00:26:13,840
Chae Hwa Young. Your days are numbered.

428
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:19,020
Once we prove they're twins,
we'll get to kick her out of this house,

429
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:22,090
and then Dream will be ours
for the taking.

430
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,490
It's here.

431
00:26:25,490 --> 00:26:28,160
- Mom, I'll go get the results.
- Okay.

432
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:37,870
(Genos Gene Examination Center)

433
00:26:37,930 --> 00:26:38,940
Thank you.

434
00:26:43,010 --> 00:26:44,010
Mom.

435
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:52,180
Are you sure you used
the right toothbrushes for the test?

436
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:53,980
Of course. You saw me do it.

437
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:55,950
Okay, let's see.

438
00:26:58,090 --> 00:27:00,590
Chae Hwa Young, you're finished.

439
00:27:03,060 --> 00:27:04,690
(Genos Gene Examination Center)

440
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,030
- One,
- One,

441
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:07,860
- two,
- two,

442
00:27:08,570 --> 00:27:09,600
- three!
- three!

443
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,350
(The First Man)

444
00:27:30,520 --> 00:27:32,490
I'm planning to marry you soon,
Director Ma.

445
00:27:32,560 --> 00:27:35,160
I don't want to.
I'm not interested in you anymore.

446
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,660
Is it because of my brother?

447
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:40,000
I snuck into Oh Jang Mi's house
and took this picture.

448
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,330
Oh Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin are twins.

449
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:44,400
This is Oh Jang Mi, right?

450
00:27:45,040 --> 00:27:46,540
I'm going to marry Director Ma Seo Rin.

451
00:27:46,840 --> 00:27:47,840
What?

452
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:49,070
Stop hitting on Seo Rin.

453
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:51,780
You're in love with Oh Jang Mi,
aren't you?

454
00:27:52,410 --> 00:27:54,440
Ms. Oh Jang Mi just moved her finger.

455
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:56,080
It looks like she's starting to wake up.

456
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:57,810
I understand. I'll be right there.

457
00:28:02,290 --> 00:28:04,290
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
